1. Bootstrap the first control-plane
If this is your first control-plane node, you need to run:

talosctl apply-config --nodes 192.168.0.110 --file clusterconfig/a/cla-cla-cp01.yaml --insecure  
talosctl apply-config --nodes 192.168.0.113 --file clusterconfig/a/cla-cla-wk01.yaml --insecure

mkdir -p $HOME/.talos
cp clusterconfig/talosconfig $HOME/.talos/cla

talosctl bootstrap \
  --nodes 192.168.0.110 \
  --config $HOME/.talos/cla

